data.name: AssociateInterstateRequest1
data.value: update CKT_INTERSTAT_RQST set CAS_I_NUMBER = @casINumber where IDENTIFIER = @identifier

data.name: AssociateInterstateRequest2
data.value: update CKT_INTERSTAT_RQST set CAS_NUMBER = @casNumber, CSP_NUMBER = @cspNumber, CRO_TYPE = @croType, CRO_ID = @croId where IDENTIFIER = @identifier

data.name: CreateInterstateRequest
ReadAbsentParentCsePerson
data.value: select top(1) CAS_NUMBER, CSP_NUMBER, TYPE, CASE_ROLE_ID, START_DATE, END_DATE from CKT_CASE_ROLE where (@casNumber = CAS_NUMBER) and (START_DATE <= @startDate) and (END_DATE > @startDate) and (CSP_NUMBER = @cspNumber)

data.name: ReadCase
data.value: select top(1) NUMB, CSE_OPEN_DATE from CKT_CASE where NUMB = @numb

data.name: ReadInterstateRequest1
data.value: select top(1) IDENTIFIER, OTHER_STATE_CAS_ID, OTHR_STATE_FIPS_CD, CREATED_BY, CREATED_TIMESTAMP, LAST_UPDATED_BY, LAST_UPDATED_TMST, OTH_ST_CASE_STATUS, CASE_TYPE, KS_CASE_IND, OTH_STATE_CLS_RES, OTH_STATE_CLS_DTE, CAS_I_NUMBER, CAS_NUMBER, CSP_NUMBER, CRO_TYPE, CRO_ID, COUNTRY from CKT_INTERSTAT_RQST order by IDENTIFIER desc

data.name: ReadInterstateRequest2
data.value: select top(1) IDENTIFIER, OTHER_STATE_CAS_ID, OTHR_STATE_FIPS_CD, CREATED_BY, CREATED_TIMESTAMP, LAST_UPDATED_BY, LAST_UPDATED_TMST, OTH_ST_CASE_STATUS, CASE_TYPE, KS_CASE_IND, OTH_STATE_CLS_RES, OTH_STATE_CLS_DTE, CAS_I_NUMBER, CAS_NUMBER, CSP_NUMBER, CRO_TYPE, CRO_ID, COUNTRY from CKT_INTERSTAT_RQST where (@casINumber = CAS_I_NUMBER) and (@croId = CRO_ID) and (@croType = CRO_TYPE) and (@cspNumber = CSP_NUMBER) and (@casNumber = CAS_NUMBER) and (OTHR_STATE_FIPS_CD = @othrStateFipsCd)
